{"tid":1245082,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"草泥馬林奠壞我排毒大計","createTime":"2019-06-20T07:21:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T14:20:17.000Z","uid":265884,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3ca3903dc7b1c3628eef811ac88c73a2e300295a","tid":1245082,"uid":265884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T07:21:18.000Z","msg":"我台灣人<br />\n本來打算6月要去香港排毒一下<br />\n發洩累積已久的壓力<br />\n結果你他媽的<br />\n跑出一個月鵝<br />\n一直在那邊給我搞事<br />\n把香港弄的亂哄哄的<br />\n這要是在台灣早就被我們扔到海裡去了<br />\n還給你在那邊身為母親講一堆鬼話<br />\n今天特地辦一個連登帳號<br />\n就是想來跟香港阿鵝喊話<br />\n媽的五點前趕快出來面對<br />\n我已經忍很久，再不排毒就要掛了<br />\n六月沒剩幾天，拜託別再鬧了<br />\n速速撤回條例啊啊啊啊啊你媽的"},{"pid":"fba3b0be948aedb47758ee89c7c7f6bef22b8a7c","tid":1245082,"uid":209294,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T07:27:38.000Z","msg":"那你可以卦了"},{"pid":"94e579b391ae3f3e6f8dd9c8968cd3a82e7e612f","tid":1245082,"uid":216127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T14:19:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"765c60c16c3cd360305156aa4278465b3fc44151","tid":1245082,"uid":68220,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T14:20:17.000Z","msg":"排不了毒就台獨一下<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n港台一家親<br />\n期待回歸中華民國"}]}